#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_graphedit.rst:14
msgid ""
"GraphEdit is an area capable of showing various GraphNodes. It manages "
"connection events between them."
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_graphedit.rst:17
msgid "Description"
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_graphedit.rst:19
msgid ""
"GraphEdit manages the showing of GraphNodes it contains, as well as "
"connections and disconnections between them. Signals are sent for each of"
" these two events. Disconnection between GraphNode slots is disabled by "
"default."
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_graphedit.rst:21
msgid ""
